WEBVTT

01:19.400 --> 01:20.660
What are you looking at

01:20.840 --> 01:21.640
so intently?

01:23.520 --> 01:26.160
I'm looking at the droplets on this lotus leaf.

01:28.120 --> 01:28.600
Look.

01:29.280 --> 01:32.240
A small droplet is a small world.

01:33.000 --> 01:34.880
Many droplets gather together

01:35.160 --> 01:36.720
to form a bigger world.

01:37.720 --> 01:39.000
These small droplets,

01:39.000 --> 01:40.560
like knights,

01:41.320 --> 01:43.000
slowly gather together,

01:43.400 --> 01:44.160
and then

01:44.200 --> 01:45.240
charge downward.

01:57.440 --> 01:58.440
I'm sorry.

01:59.240 --> 02:01.040
Am I acting a bit weird?

02:03.840 --> 02:05.120
Actually,

02:05.960 --> 02:08.220
I wouldn't usually notice these things.

02:11.840 --> 02:13.680
I got sick a lot when I was a kid.

02:14.960 --> 02:16.440
When getting IV drips,

02:16.960 --> 02:18.440
I had nothing else to do.

02:19.680 --> 02:21.400
So I lay in the hospital bed

02:21.720 --> 02:24.380
and watched the little water drops on the IV bag.

02:24.800 --> 02:26.520
Maybe starting from then,

02:27.400 --> 02:28.680
I often observe things

02:28.680 --> 02:30.200
that others wouldn't.

02:32.200 --> 02:32.840
Like what?

02:39.920 --> 02:41.380
Like the clouds in the sky.

02:46.160 --> 02:48.800
I used to think clouds were only one color.

02:49.920 --> 02:51.560
Now, after observing,

02:51.840 --> 02:53.880
I realize they can be pink,

02:54.040 --> 02:54.800
yellow,

02:55.200 --> 02:55.960
purple,

02:56.840 --> 02:59.280
or even black and gray.

03:00.440 --> 03:01.600
Different clouds

03:02.200 --> 03:03.640
have different stories.

03:07.480 --> 03:08.540
Look at that cloud.

03:13.480 --> 03:16.140
Doesn't it look like a mother dog with her puppy?

03:29.160 --> 03:30.240
And this shed.

03:31.960 --> 03:33.680
Whenever the wind blows,

03:33.920 --> 03:35.120
it looks like

03:35.120 --> 03:37.040
many people are dancing the hula.

03:45.040 --> 03:46.680
Am I being a bit childish?

03:47.640 --> 03:48.240
No.

03:49.960 --> 03:51.490
That's quite interesting.

03:53.400 --> 03:54.079
Thank you.

04:17.800 --> 04:18.600
You're back.

04:19.720 --> 04:20.640
Xiaocen,

04:21.600 --> 04:22.400
you're back.

04:24.520 --> 04:25.880
Mom, you startled me.

04:25.880 --> 04:28.560
Don't you recognize your mom just because she has a face mask on?

04:28.560 --> 04:29.800
Why are you back so late?

04:29.800 --> 04:31.600
You didn't answer your phone either.

04:31.600 --> 04:33.760
I turned on Do Not Disturb during class

04:34.040 --> 04:35.440
and forgot to turn it off.

04:35.440 --> 04:37.560
What were you playing until so late?

04:37.800 --> 04:39.080
Just eating.

04:39.120 --> 04:41.240
Eating until so late? This kid.

04:41.760 --> 04:42.400
Xiaocen,

04:42.760 --> 04:44.760
come, let Aunt put a face mask on you.

04:45.040 --> 04:46.840
I'll pass. I'm going back first.

04:47.400 --> 04:47.960
All right.

04:47.960 --> 04:48.680
Xiaocen,

04:49.400 --> 04:50.860
what did you forget again?

04:50.880 --> 04:52.880
I heated this medicine for you twice

04:52.960 --> 04:53.960
before you came back.

04:53.960 --> 04:56.000
Mom, I know how to heat it myself.

04:59.840 --> 05:01.640
Sit down. Drink it before you go.

05:41.360 --> 05:42.200
Jingdezhen

05:42.760 --> 05:44.820
used to be the site of imperial kilns.

05:45.240 --> 05:47.720
Only the finest top-tier porcelain

05:48.080 --> 05:49.680
would be selected and sent to the capital.

05:49.680 --> 05:50.540
As for the rest,

05:52.159 --> 05:53.960
to prevent them from circulating among the public,

05:53.960 --> 05:56.420
they were all smashed and buried on the spot.

05:56.520 --> 05:57.720
So in Jingdezhen,

05:58.680 --> 06:00.720
around many ancient kiln ruins,

06:01.400 --> 06:02.880
there are large amounts of

06:03.200 --> 06:04.860
ancient porcelain fragments

06:05.000 --> 06:05.680
piled up.

06:08.600 --> 06:09.200
All right.

06:09.480 --> 06:10.480
Please be seated.

06:14.200 --> 06:15.200
In Jingdezhen,

06:15.400 --> 06:17.680
the place where you encounter the most ancient porcelain

06:17.680 --> 06:18.680
is Antique City.

06:19.000 --> 06:21.720
There are imperial kilns and folk kilns from past dynasties,

06:21.720 --> 06:22.360
as well as

06:22.400 --> 06:25.400
various blue-and-white porcelain and famille rose.

06:26.200 --> 06:28.200
Antique City was originally called

06:28.360 --> 06:29.160
the ghost market.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.040
A ghost market?

06:30.800 --> 06:31.800
Is it haunted?

06:32.520 --> 06:33.450
The ghost market

06:33.480 --> 06:35.840
was formed in the 1990s.

06:36.080 --> 06:37.960
Its scale grew larger and larger.

06:38.680 --> 06:40.800
At that time, every Monday,

06:41.200 --> 06:42.200
the market opened in the early morning.

06:42.200 --> 06:43.680
The goods sold are of unknown origin,

06:43.680 --> 06:44.640
and it disperses at dawn.

06:44.640 --> 06:45.159
So,

06:45.360 --> 06:46.560
it got the name,

06:46.640 --> 06:47.920
called the ghost market.

06:47.920 --> 06:49.120
Now these stalls

06:49.120 --> 06:51.960
have all moved to the porcelain sculpture factory.

06:51.960 --> 06:53.090
I will take everyone

06:53.280 --> 06:54.940
to the site for some practice.

07:03.840 --> 07:04.570
How about it?

07:05.480 --> 07:06.280
Is everyone here?

07:06.280 --> 07:06.960
We're here.

07:06.960 --> 07:07.440
We're here.

07:07.440 --> 07:09.200
This is the Porcelain Sculpture Factory.

07:09.200 --> 07:11.640
Your task is to pick a piece

07:12.600 --> 07:14.520
of ancient porcelain from before the Republic of China.

07:14.520 --> 07:15.880
Will it be very expensive?

07:15.880 --> 07:16.520
Usually,

07:16.840 --> 07:18.800
you can get it for under 100 yuan.

07:19.200 --> 07:20.800
That seems affordable.

07:21.400 --> 07:22.560
Don't let your guard down.

07:22.560 --> 07:24.800
Every stall owner here says

07:24.960 --> 07:26.120
that the items on their stall

07:26.120 --> 07:28.240
are authentic antiques.

07:28.600 --> 07:29.240
However,

07:29.520 --> 07:31.840
there are many fakes mixed in.

07:32.120 --> 07:32.760
This time,

07:32.880 --> 07:34.480
it's a test of your judgment.

07:34.760 --> 07:35.240
Got it?

07:35.920 --> 07:36.450
Let's go.

07:36.560 --> 07:37.360
Let's go.

07:37.360 --> 07:38.490
Let's go take a look.

07:38.760 --> 07:39.800
Let's see who picks first.

07:39.800 --> 07:40.200
Let's go.

07:40.200 --> 07:40.560
Let's go together.

07:40.560 --> 07:40.960
Go.

07:43.000 --> 07:44.400
Yuexin, look at this.

07:56.200 --> 07:56.760
Mr. Yue,

07:57.200 --> 07:58.360
help me take a look at this piece.

07:58.360 --> 07:59.360
Is it real or fake?

08:01.240 --> 08:02.360
See for yourself.

08:04.080 --> 08:04.720
Come and take a look.

08:04.720 --> 08:06.050
Pick whatever you like.

08:15.680 --> 08:17.080
Handsome, come take a look.

08:17.080 --> 08:19.410
These are all Song Dynasty qingbai wares.

08:22.200 --> 08:23.480
I like this one.

08:24.200 --> 08:25.560
Is this real?

08:42.600 --> 08:44.000
Feel free to look around.

08:55.800 --> 08:56.400
Student.

08:57.480 --> 08:58.880
Look at these blue-and-white porcelain shards.

08:58.880 --> 09:01.800
I have them from the Yuan Dynasty to the Qing Dynasty here.

09:01.800 --> 09:03.130
Guaranteed authentic.

09:04.520 --> 09:06.400
How did you know I was a student?

09:06.720 --> 09:08.120
With these eyes of mine,

09:08.400 --> 09:10.640
go ask around in this ghost market.

09:15.560 --> 09:17.620
They are all very pretty. Have a look.

09:22.400 --> 09:23.000
Miss,

09:23.120 --> 09:24.180
you have a good eye.

09:25.160 --> 09:27.120
This is from the Qianlong period.

09:27.520 --> 09:29.760
A conical bowl with pine, bamboo, and plum blossom patterns.

09:29.760 --> 09:31.160
Absolutely a good piece.

09:31.440 --> 09:32.120
The style,

09:32.640 --> 09:33.440
and the glaze.

09:35.360 --> 09:36.720
When it comes to blue-and-white porcelain,

09:36.720 --> 09:38.680
I am the best in Jingdezhen.

09:38.960 --> 09:40.360
Even across the country,

09:40.360 --> 09:41.360
I have few rivals.

09:42.320 --> 09:43.360
I know Jingdezhen

09:43.360 --> 09:44.680
is full of hidden talents.

09:44.680 --> 09:45.440
Exactly.

09:46.480 --> 09:48.640
Picking blue-and-white porcelain fragments,

09:48.640 --> 09:50.480
it's all about one thing:

09:50.880 --> 09:51.480
destiny.

09:51.920 --> 09:53.380
You came to my little shop,

09:53.480 --> 09:55.000
looked at these fragments,

09:55.000 --> 09:56.400
and picked this one.

09:56.680 --> 09:57.940
It was unintentional,

09:59.080 --> 10:00.600
but meant to be.

10:01.120 --> 10:01.980
Let me tell you,

10:02.120 --> 10:03.240
every fragment

10:03.600 --> 10:05.840
has its destined owner.

10:06.720 --> 10:07.800
The one you are holding,

10:07.800 --> 10:08.560
its owner

10:09.120 --> 10:09.920
is you.

10:14.120 --> 10:16.120
I still don't quite understand you.

10:16.600 --> 10:18.480
But this piece is really nice.

10:18.480 --> 10:19.680
How is it? You like it?

10:20.480 --> 10:20.960
Sir,

10:21.720 --> 10:22.520
how much is it?

10:22.640 --> 10:23.920
If it were anyone else,

10:24.520 --> 10:25.560
they wouldn't get it

10:25.560 --> 10:26.960
without a thousand yuan.

10:27.040 --> 10:27.680
But

10:28.000 --> 10:29.440
since you have a connection with it,

10:29.440 --> 10:30.520
and you are a student,

10:30.520 --> 10:31.680
I'll give you a student discount.

10:31.680 --> 10:32.360
Nine hundred and fifty.

10:32.360 --> 10:32.800
Deal?

10:35.600 --> 10:37.060
It's still too expensive.

10:40.560 --> 10:41.040
Miss.

10:41.200 --> 10:41.800
Miss!

10:42.240 --> 10:43.120
Wait a minute.

10:43.760 --> 10:45.480
We are so connected,

10:46.880 --> 10:48.160
how much can you offer?

10:49.040 --> 10:49.770
Two hundred.

10:55.160 --> 10:55.680
Miss,

10:57.120 --> 10:57.980
three hundred.

10:58.720 --> 11:00.160
Deal. Thank you, Sir.

11:05.600 --> 11:06.680
Sir, I've transferred the money.

11:06.680 --> 11:07.400
All right.

11:07.800 --> 11:08.400
Of course,

11:08.560 --> 11:09.520
I hope

11:09.760 --> 11:11.000
young people like you

11:11.160 --> 11:12.520
can help us

11:12.920 --> 11:14.280
promote

11:14.520 --> 11:15.920
our Chinese ceramics.

11:16.520 --> 11:17.380
Thank you, Sir.

11:18.040 --> 11:20.900
Otherwise, I won't be able to explain to my teacher.

11:21.520 --> 11:22.120
Miss,

11:22.560 --> 11:23.620
where do you study?

11:23.760 --> 11:25.960
I am at Jingdezhen Ceramic University.

11:26.280 --> 11:27.000
What major?

11:27.480 --> 11:30.210
Freshman, Cultural Relics Conservation major.

11:31.640 --> 11:32.200
Is

11:33.280 --> 11:35.040
Yue Qixin your teacher?

11:36.000 --> 11:36.560
Yes.

11:36.880 --> 11:38.010
Sir, do you know him?

11:40.520 --> 11:41.240
Sort of.

11:50.240 --> 11:51.120
Sir, then

11:51.520 --> 11:52.520
I'll get going.

11:53.760 --> 11:54.200
Okay.

11:54.440 --> 11:55.160
Take care.

11:56.360 --> 11:56.840
Okay.

11:58.200 --> 11:58.680
Miss!

12:03.840 --> 12:04.440
Well,

12:05.160 --> 12:06.720
come visit often.

12:07.960 --> 12:08.560
Come often.

12:08.560 --> 12:09.160
Goodbye.

12:09.640 --> 12:10.170
Goodbye.

12:25.200 --> 12:26.560
Let me help you

12:26.560 --> 12:27.560
check your choices.

12:27.560 --> 12:28.280
Okay.

12:29.120 --> 12:31.200
Don't cry if you picked a fake.

12:32.760 --> 12:33.800
Mine can't be fake.

12:33.800 --> 12:34.600
Mr. Yue, look.

12:34.800 --> 12:36.040
The vendor said it's Qing dynasty famille rose.

12:36.040 --> 12:36.800
Is it?

12:36.800 --> 12:37.520
What do you mean, he said?

12:37.520 --> 12:38.040
What did you buy?

12:38.040 --> 12:39.760
Don't you have the ability to distinguish?

12:39.760 --> 12:42.560
A piece of Qianlong era blue-and-white porcelain.

12:42.560 --> 12:43.160
Let me see.

12:44.000 --> 12:45.600
Mr. Yue, can you look at mine?

12:47.560 --> 12:49.680
The painting and details are very refined.

12:49.680 --> 12:50.200
Not bad.

12:50.640 --> 12:52.320
It should be Qianlong era blue-and-white porcelain.

12:52.320 --> 12:53.800
You met a good seller.

12:55.040 --> 12:55.840
Okay, thank you, Mr. Yue.

12:55.840 --> 12:56.320
Wait a moment.

12:56.320 --> 12:57.050
Compare them

12:57.600 --> 12:59.240
and see what the difference is.

12:59.240 --> 12:59.720
Okay.

13:05.680 --> 13:07.210
Qing dynasty famille rose.

13:07.960 --> 13:09.240
Very pretty. Not bad.

13:09.400 --> 13:10.460
Thank you, Mr. Yue.

13:11.800 --> 13:13.000
Mr. Yue, look at mine.

13:13.120 --> 13:13.720
Let me see.

13:14.000 --> 13:14.840
Yours

13:15.640 --> 13:16.700
is obviously fake.

13:16.800 --> 13:17.440
Fake?

13:18.080 --> 13:19.360
But the vendor said it's Ru kiln.

13:19.360 --> 13:20.120
Ru kiln?

13:20.360 --> 13:21.440
If it were really Ru kiln,

13:21.440 --> 13:22.680
you'd have made a fortune.

13:22.680 --> 13:24.000
I spent 300 yuan on it.

13:24.800 --> 13:26.000
Mr. Yue, 800 yuan.

13:26.080 --> 13:26.680
This one

13:27.200 --> 13:28.360
is worth 100 yuan.

13:28.440 --> 13:29.000
Take it.

13:30.080 --> 13:30.680
Students,

13:31.280 --> 13:32.120
did you see that?

13:32.120 --> 13:33.480
If your skills aren't good enough,

13:33.480 --> 13:34.610
you will lose money.

13:35.800 --> 13:36.800
This one,

13:37.720 --> 13:41.120
with pine, bamboo, and plum patterns, from the Qianlong era.

13:42.040 --> 13:42.520
Wait.

13:46.440 --> 13:48.320
Even I was almost fooled.

13:48.600 --> 13:49.530
This one of yours

13:50.080 --> 13:50.760
is a fake.

13:52.280 --> 13:53.040
Nowadays,

13:53.280 --> 13:54.560
in the Antique City,

13:54.800 --> 13:57.280
making small money with such high-imitation craftsmanship,

13:57.280 --> 13:58.680
there's only one person.

13:59.360 --> 13:59.800
Who is it?

13:59.800 --> 14:00.440
Students,

14:00.880 --> 14:02.560
talk to each other,

14:02.640 --> 14:04.280
look and compare,

14:04.560 --> 14:05.760
and learn from one another.

14:05.760 --> 14:07.290
The teacher said it's fake.

14:09.680 --> 14:10.480
Throw it away.

14:12.120 --> 14:14.000
But I think it looks nice.

14:14.280 --> 14:15.160
Fake is fake.

14:34.800 --> 14:36.840
It's a really good imitation.

14:37.720 --> 14:38.720
Selling for 300.

14:38.840 --> 14:40.080
It's not a rip-off.

14:50.760 --> 14:51.890
Come home tomorrow.

14:52.160 --> 14:53.760
I have something to tell you.

15:01.360 --> 15:02.600
I don't want to go to class.

15:02.600 --> 15:03.400
Hurry up.

15:03.880 --> 15:07.240
You have personally visited the antique market.

15:07.360 --> 15:08.840
Everyone must have felt it.

15:08.840 --> 15:10.360
To appraise antique porcelain.

15:10.360 --> 15:11.090
First of all,

15:11.680 --> 15:12.810
you must understand

15:13.480 --> 15:15.740
the origin of antique-style porcelain.

15:16.200 --> 15:18.280
The first step in making antique-style porcelain

15:18.280 --> 15:19.320
is to sketch on the ceramics,

15:19.320 --> 15:20.380
Pass it over there.

15:20.560 --> 15:24.040
depicting classic decorative patterns.

15:24.320 --> 15:25.000
Today,

15:25.160 --> 15:27.800
I am distributing these ceramic bisques to you.

15:27.800 --> 15:29.360
I want you all

15:30.000 --> 15:31.400
to paint on these bisques

15:31.400 --> 15:32.400
using colors

15:32.720 --> 15:35.650
to create imitation Yuan blue-and-white patterns.

15:35.800 --> 15:36.840
Pay attention, everyone.

15:36.840 --> 15:40.200
They must be imitation Yuan blue-and-white patterns.

15:40.360 --> 15:42.520
Hand them in to me after you finish painting.

15:42.520 --> 15:43.080
I will

15:43.200 --> 15:45.560
put them in the electric kiln to fire,

15:46.640 --> 15:48.170
and then return them to you.

15:48.480 --> 15:50.560
I will score and grade your work.

15:50.560 --> 15:51.360
Is that clear?

15:51.400 --> 15:52.440
Clear.

16:48.840 --> 16:50.880
I went to the old house to clean up today.

16:50.880 --> 16:51.720
Take a look at these.

16:51.720 --> 16:53.520
Is there anything else you want?

17:22.599 --> 17:25.530
Do you still care so much about that person's things?

17:25.680 --> 17:27.280
Do you think he'll come back?

17:27.400 --> 17:27.880
I don't.

17:33.360 --> 17:35.360
Then why did you choose this major?

17:36.280 --> 17:37.440
Do you think our family

17:37.440 --> 17:38.400
hasn't suffered enough

17:38.400 --> 17:39.440
from this?

17:44.840 --> 17:45.840
For so many years,

17:46.520 --> 17:48.180
he hasn't come back to see you.

17:48.680 --> 17:50.280
Do you really not resent him?

18:56.280 --> 18:57.160
Yuexin.

18:58.520 --> 18:59.240
Xiaocen.

19:02.160 --> 19:02.760
Xiaocen.

19:02.800 --> 19:05.360
I didn't expect you to like playing claw machines.

19:05.360 --> 19:06.840
When I go shopping at the mall,

19:06.840 --> 19:07.880
I come here to play.

19:07.880 --> 19:08.480
Really?

19:08.480 --> 19:09.160
That's great.

19:09.160 --> 19:10.640
We can come together next time.

19:10.640 --> 19:11.040
Okay.

19:11.040 --> 19:12.120
Because Wu Jing and Yan Xue,

19:12.120 --> 19:13.520
neither of them wants to come with me.

19:13.520 --> 19:15.180
They think it's too childish.

19:16.960 --> 19:17.520
Xiaocen.

19:18.000 --> 19:19.860
Why did you only get so few tokens?

19:20.160 --> 19:22.420
I just bought a few to satisfy my craving.

19:22.640 --> 19:24.170
How can that be satisfying?

19:24.400 --> 19:25.680
I'll share some with you.

19:25.680 --> 19:26.440
No, thanks.

19:27.080 --> 19:28.120
Coin inserted successfully.

19:28.120 --> 19:29.380
Please start the game.

19:36.200 --> 19:36.800
Let's grab this one.

19:36.800 --> 19:37.280
Okay.

19:39.280 --> 19:39.880
Good luck!

19:43.680 --> 19:44.520
Awesome!

19:44.640 --> 19:45.520
Awesome!

19:46.240 --> 19:47.840
Play again?

19:52.360 --> 19:53.760
Let's go somewhere else.

19:53.800 --> 19:54.360
Okay.

19:57.560 --> 19:58.480
Coin inserted.

19:58.480 --> 19:59.920
Please hurry up.

20:02.080 --> 20:03.400
Almost got it!

20:06.480 --> 20:07.940
How are you so good at this?

20:08.160 --> 20:09.420
Do you have any tricks?

20:09.560 --> 20:10.420
It's just luck.

20:10.640 --> 20:12.400
Some people can never catch anything,

20:12.400 --> 20:14.260
but some catch it on the first try.

20:19.560 --> 20:20.690
Let's keep playing.

20:25.440 --> 20:26.240
What's wrong?

20:30.680 --> 20:32.800
It's definitely not about luck.

20:33.560 --> 20:34.800
There's a trick to it.

20:35.000 --> 20:36.600
She's taking advantage of you.

20:36.600 --> 20:37.660
Taking advantage?

20:39.040 --> 20:41.400
Actually, there's a strategy to claw machines.

20:41.400 --> 20:42.260
What strategy?

20:43.000 --> 20:44.080
Generally speaking,

20:44.080 --> 20:46.000
for the first seven or eight tries,

20:46.000 --> 20:47.260
the claw is very loose.

20:47.400 --> 20:48.960
So our chances of catching one are very low.

20:48.960 --> 20:50.120
Then there will be one or two tries

20:50.120 --> 20:51.640
when the claw is very tight.

20:51.640 --> 20:54.240
The chances of catching one are very high then.

20:54.600 --> 20:55.320
This girl,

20:55.320 --> 20:57.880
she always waits for you to fail before she tries.

20:57.880 --> 20:59.680
So it's easy for her to catch one.

20:59.840 --> 21:01.160
How do you know so much?

21:01.320 --> 21:03.920
Because I often stake out others like that too.

21:04.120 --> 21:05.240
Really?

21:06.800 --> 21:07.280
Also,

21:07.560 --> 21:09.960
you can wait until the staff restocks the machine.

21:09.960 --> 21:11.520
They put the dolls on the edge,

21:11.520 --> 21:13.400
which makes it very easy to catch them.

21:13.400 --> 21:15.040
And when you grab the doll, don't grab its head.

21:15.040 --> 21:15.840
Grab its body.

21:15.840 --> 21:17.300
It holds tighter that way.

21:20.360 --> 21:22.290
Why are you looking at me like that?

21:24.000 --> 21:25.240
You know what, Xiaocen?

21:25.240 --> 21:26.560
Since the beginning of school,

21:26.560 --> 21:27.800
everything you've said to me

21:27.800 --> 21:28.520
doesn't add up to

21:28.520 --> 21:29.850
what you just said to me.

21:31.800 --> 21:32.440
I'm sorry.

21:32.440 --> 21:34.400
Did I say too much just now?

21:34.400 --> 21:35.240
Did I annoy you?

21:35.240 --> 21:36.280
Don't be sorry.

21:36.400 --> 21:37.440
You were very cute just now.

21:37.440 --> 21:38.240
I really like it.

21:38.240 --> 21:39.370
Talk more next time.

21:39.560 --> 21:40.760
Thank you, Yuexin.

21:40.960 --> 21:41.890
You're welcome.

21:51.480 --> 21:52.140
Here you go.

21:53.880 --> 21:54.280
Again.

21:54.320 --> 21:56.980
Hello. What can I exchange these four dolls for?

21:57.360 --> 21:58.520
Four dolls.

21:59.440 --> 22:01.700
You can exchange them for this keychain.

22:03.880 --> 22:05.320
Hello, I am a member.

22:05.440 --> 22:06.280
Please check.

22:06.280 --> 22:07.520
With the ones I saved here before

22:07.520 --> 22:10.120
and these four dolls, what can I exchange them for?

22:10.120 --> 22:11.080
This big doll.

22:13.600 --> 22:14.480
I'll take this one.

22:14.480 --> 22:14.810
Okay.

22:16.680 --> 22:18.080
Xiaocen, this is for you.

22:19.240 --> 22:19.960
No need.

22:19.960 --> 22:21.720
You caught most of these dolls.

22:22.000 --> 22:23.520
There's no room for them on my bed.

22:23.520 --> 22:24.720
Since I can't take them back to the dorm,

22:24.720 --> 22:25.980
you can take them back.

22:26.120 --> 22:27.120
Thank you, Yuexin.

22:27.120 --> 22:28.050
You're welcome.

22:32.400 --> 22:33.840
Can you hurry up?

22:33.840 --> 22:36.170
You've been looking at it for half an hour.

22:38.840 --> 22:39.600
You're back.

22:40.160 --> 22:43.000
Sister, you're finally back.

22:43.320 --> 22:44.600
Sister, what did you bring?

22:44.600 --> 22:45.530
A little rabbit.

22:46.240 --> 22:47.360
What are you holding?

22:47.360 --> 22:49.020
I caught it with my classmate.

22:49.120 --> 22:51.000
Sister, isn't this for me?

22:51.000 --> 22:52.400
How could it be for you?

22:52.400 --> 22:54.130
You two, come here and sit down.

23:00.640 --> 23:01.640
Who gave it to you?

23:02.000 --> 23:03.360
A boy or a girl?

23:04.160 --> 23:05.840
Mom, a girl.

23:05.960 --> 23:06.760
I'll show you.

23:07.160 --> 23:08.600
She's our class monitor.

23:08.960 --> 23:11.160
We went to the claw machine after class.

23:12.800 --> 23:15.240
You are getting along well with your classmates now.

23:15.240 --> 23:15.970
That's good.

23:17.080 --> 23:19.740
Why are you looking at me? Look at the questions.

23:21.480 --> 23:24.840
Please no, I'm too tired, Aunt.

23:25.840 --> 23:27.970
How about we go pick up my mom from work?

23:28.040 --> 23:28.600
Sit down.

23:33.480 --> 23:36.000
You are full of excuses, aren't you?

23:36.760 --> 23:38.480
I don't usually see you being this filial.

23:38.480 --> 23:39.240
Trying to slack off.

23:39.240 --> 23:40.680
Sister is back.

23:40.680 --> 23:42.960
Auntie, go tutor her.

23:43.160 --> 23:44.560
My eyes hurt.

23:44.560 --> 23:46.200
I'll lie down for a bit.

23:46.600 --> 23:47.800
Get up, get up, get up.

23:47.960 --> 23:48.760
Sit properly.

23:49.160 --> 23:51.200
Your mom spoils you, but I won't.

23:51.320 --> 23:52.960
Do you know how competitive it is now?

23:52.960 --> 23:54.040
If you don't study hard now,

23:54.040 --> 23:55.680
what good school can you get into when you grow up?

23:55.680 --> 23:56.610
Ask your sister.

23:57.040 --> 23:58.840
Hasn't she been through this since she was little?

23:58.840 --> 23:59.280
Yes.

24:00.120 --> 24:00.680
Right?

24:00.760 --> 24:01.160
Yes.

24:02.680 --> 24:03.680
Did you hear that?

24:06.200 --> 24:09.040
You must finish this set of questions today.

24:14.800 --> 24:15.680
Well,

24:16.400 --> 24:18.000
can I excuse myself now?

24:20.560 --> 24:21.320
Go.

24:23.800 --> 24:25.660
I'll cut some fruit for you later.

24:28.840 --> 24:31.480
There's definitely something going on between them.

24:31.480 --> 24:32.400
I think,

24:32.800 --> 24:34.460
at this stage of the semester,

24:34.800 --> 24:37.360
any potential couples have already paired up.

24:37.360 --> 24:40.200
Anyway, I don't think the guys in our class are good enough.

24:40.200 --> 24:41.360
It's not that they're not good enough.

24:41.360 --> 24:42.280
I just feel like

24:42.400 --> 24:43.520
dating in college is unreliable.

24:43.520 --> 24:44.480
Then who do you think,

24:44.480 --> 24:45.810
if we rate them by looks,

24:46.160 --> 24:47.400
among the boys in our class,

24:47.400 --> 24:48.800
is the most handsome?

24:49.000 --> 24:50.120
Don't you think

24:50.160 --> 24:51.880
Li Zhuoting is quite cute?

24:54.720 --> 24:56.080
Are you serious?

24:56.200 --> 24:57.360
Are you okay?

24:58.240 --> 25:00.400
He follows Wang Lin around every day.

25:01.000 --> 25:01.520
Wang Lin?

25:01.520 --> 25:03.480
Never mind, don't mention Wang Lin.

25:03.480 --> 25:05.360
Those two are birds of a feather.

25:06.080 --> 25:07.400
But don't you think

25:07.560 --> 25:09.400
he looks shy when he smiles?

25:09.680 --> 25:11.000
Are you okay?

25:11.400 --> 25:12.400
In terms of looks,

25:12.400 --> 25:14.120
Xu Xiao is definitely ranked ahead of them.

25:14.120 --> 25:15.000
Exactly.

25:15.120 --> 25:16.640
But Xu Xiao and Zhao Xiaocen

25:16.640 --> 25:18.400
always go to classes together.

25:18.400 --> 25:19.000
Right.

25:19.240 --> 25:20.480
I've seen them leaving school

25:20.480 --> 25:21.440
together several times.

25:21.440 --> 25:23.080
So are they really a thing?

25:23.080 --> 25:23.760
I think so.

25:23.800 --> 25:24.720
Definitely.

25:25.040 --> 25:26.840
Then that's so unfair to Yuexin.

25:27.080 --> 25:28.280
If we're talking about first come, first served,

25:28.280 --> 25:29.480
Yuexin should be first.

25:29.480 --> 25:29.840
I...

25:29.840 --> 25:30.720
Right.

25:30.960 --> 25:31.520
This...

25:31.520 --> 25:32.240
What are you doing?

25:32.240 --> 25:33.480
Don't deny it.

25:33.640 --> 25:34.720
During military training,

25:34.720 --> 25:36.160
didn't we already interrogate you?

25:36.160 --> 25:37.000
Yeah.

25:37.000 --> 25:37.400
No.

25:37.400 --> 25:38.280
You just have a crush on Xu Xiao.

25:38.280 --> 25:39.000
No.

25:39.000 --> 25:40.360
You guys forced me to say it.

25:40.360 --> 25:40.960
I don't.

25:41.000 --> 25:41.640
Did you ask?

25:41.640 --> 25:42.360
I didn't.

25:42.360 --> 25:43.200
Me neither.

25:43.560 --> 25:44.040
Wait.

25:44.680 --> 25:45.240
Yuexin,

25:45.600 --> 25:47.160
do you still like Xu Xiao?

25:48.280 --> 25:48.920
Don't ask that.

25:48.920 --> 25:50.980
You just have a crush on him. Admit it.

25:51.320 --> 25:53.000
If they're not together,

25:53.440 --> 25:54.570
will you make a move?

25:57.840 --> 25:59.400
It's getting late.

25:59.440 --> 26:00.760
Why don't we go to sleep?

26:00.760 --> 26:01.160
Good night.

26:01.160 --> 26:02.440
Yuexin, you're doing this again.

26:02.440 --> 26:03.440
Doing this again.

26:03.440 --> 26:04.760
Always avoiding it.

26:04.760 --> 26:05.640
Not admitting it.

26:05.640 --> 26:06.240
Yeah,

26:06.240 --> 26:07.570
what's so hard to admit?

26:07.920 --> 26:11.960
Listen, the horn of the new journey sounds.

26:12.000 --> 26:16.080
Listen, the horn of the new journey sounds.

26:16.480 --> 26:19.920
The goal of a strong army calls ahead.

26:20.200 --> 26:23.920
The goal of a strong army calls ahead.

26:43.040 --> 26:44.600
Don't forget the whole class is going tonight.

26:44.600 --> 26:45.560
Okay.

26:45.560 --> 26:46.080
Got it.

26:47.640 --> 26:49.560
Let's go buy some food first. I'm a little hungry.

26:49.560 --> 26:51.480
Is Xiaocen going to the party this time?

26:51.480 --> 26:52.210
I don't know.

26:53.920 --> 26:54.480
Xiaocen.

26:55.240 --> 26:56.570
We have a party tonight.

26:57.080 --> 26:58.560
Yuexin is a good girl.

26:59.240 --> 27:00.920
I was too passive before.
